cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper is about deep neural network (DNN) compression techniques, specifically weight pruning and weight quantization. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) since these fields heavily rely on DNNs. The paper also uses optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
